1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,040
Gloucester, Massachusetts.

2
00:00:01,340 --> 00:00:02,980
October 30th, 2001.

3
00:00:03,409 --> 00:00:04,880
2100 Hours.

4
00:00:38,350 --> 00:00:39,590
Condi, this is Fisk.

5
00:00:40,370 --> 00:00:41,470
I hope you had a safe trip.

6
00:00:42,539 --> 00:00:45,290
Now, I can already hear you ranting,
but I've taken on a new case.

7
00:00:45,291 --> 00:00:47,230
I know, I know, I promised I'd quit.

8
00:00:47,270 --> 00:00:51,570
But I was contacted by a man named Johnson
to go to Shadow Island and investigate

9
00:00:51,571 --> 00:00:53,930
Ovid Morton and the Epcanis writing
tablets.

10
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:55,430
Does that ring any bells?

11
00:00:55,910 --> 00:00:58,850
Now you understand why I couldn't say no
and had to leave right away.

12
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:00,170
I'm going tomorrow.

13
00:01:00,354 --> 00:01:02,130
I left some notes on the office desk.

14
00:01:02,899 --> 00:01:03,899
See you soon, Connie.

15
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:06,090
Oh, I nearly forgot.

16
00:01:06,510 --> 00:01:10,850
If you want to contact Johnson,
he's at 555-1495.

17
00:01:10,851 --> 00:01:11,290
.

18
00:01:11,291 --> 00:01:11,310
.

19
00:01:11,311 --> 00:01:12,750
.

20
00:01:12,750 --> 00:01:13,750
.

